Returns: List of the keys contained in this map.
getKeys().Description: Returns a list of the keys contained in this map. The list returned is not modifiable, so any attempts to modify it will throw a UnsupportedOperationException. All values retrieved by a key from this list with #get are guaranteed to be non-null. Each key is only listed once in the list. The order of the keys is undefined.

ClassDesc: The base class for camera controls and information. This class defines the basic key/value map used for querying for camera characteristics or capture results, and for setting camera request parameters. All instances of CameraMetadata are immutable. The list of keys with @B_android#hardware#camera2#CameraMetadata#getKeys_E@ never changes, nor do the values returned by any key with #get throughout the lifetime of the object.
